reviewText: Great Series. I got all four seasons. Love it.

Thank you so much. I'm every happy with the product. It got here on time and in good condition. This show is amazing I love it so much!!!

A pity that the English translation has never happened, but the sub-titles allowed me to follow the story well enough.  Saito and Louisa combine to oppose a Royal whose boredom is such that he starts a war to see if that will keep him interested.  They simultaneously have to fight off Louisa's rivals for Saito's hand - and other parts - from young noblewomen, a servant maid, an elf maid, and their own queen!  Very Enjoyable!
I'd have given it a five star if they had dubbed it to match season one. Story is great and ends the series well.
